    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348930/extras/19bfc47f6dbd272f816ad96ab3142205.webp?t=1744958119\" width=612 height=40 /></span><br><br>大混乱！微中子兵破坏了神龟们最新的披萨派对！来自X次元的神龟们急需帮助：施莱德正准备征服多元宇宙！<br><br>我们的英雄需要在不同的次元之间跳跃，并彻底阻止施莱德！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348930/extras/03e7e79a221ba0ac98ae4a5e879c2acd.poster.avif?t=1744958119\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348930/extras/03e7e79a221ba0ac98ae4a5e879c2acd.webm?t=1744958119\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348930/extras/03e7e79a221ba0ac98ae4a5e879c2acd.mp4?t=1744958119\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348930/extras/4997019ca554cd2da60be4229717a75c.webp?t=1744958119\" width=612 height=40 /></span><br><br>进入全新的游戏模式：生存模式。<br><br>一“晶”二楚！击退大脚帮大军，抢夺次元水晶！收集足够的水晶可以穿越不同的次元，追击邪恶的施莱德！<br><br>作出明智的选择。每次胜利都会产生两个传送门，提供不同的奖励。你的选择将决定你的下一场次元之战！<br>拿取特殊的披萨、获得神秘的刺激时刻，甚至化身成神龟们的最大敌人！<br><br>升级，兄弟！通过跨越次元的一次次经历变得更强大！你甚至可以一路解锁专属角色的颜色！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348930/extras/334da3d34b80340c67b943f784cc7fd6.webp?t=1744958119\" width=612 height=40 /></span><br><br>《Dimension Shellshock》带来了新的可玩战士，包括宫本兔和辛。<br><br>坚毅的兔子武士已经准备好跳越次元，与邪恶作斗争，并见证等待神龟们的一场异界全新战斗！<br><br>无论作为盟友还是敌人，辛都毫不犹豫地与神龟们一起跳进了多元宇宙的混战中！她利用闪电般的招数，为夺回大脚帮的荣誉而战！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348930/extras/75d34c71428358a710d8b134911a917b.poster.avif?t=1744958119\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348930/extras/75d34c71428358a710d8b134911a917b.webm?t=1744958119\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348930/extras/75d34c71428358a710d8b134911a917b.mp4?t=1744958119\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348930/extras/d3f672f53604afd981be6e4dfdd857a4.webp?t=1744958119\" width=612 height=40 /></span><br><br>● 在全新的生存模式中展现你的忍者技能！<br>● 收集水晶并穿越向TMNT各时代致敬的多个次元<br>● 新的可玩角色：在故事、街机和生存模式中扮演宫本兔和辛，进行战斗！<br>● Tee Lopes 的精彩新曲目！<br>● 解锁专属调色板。沿着忍者龟的记忆小巷漫步，享受新的色调！<br>● 在生存模式排行榜上通过战斗一路高升！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348930/extras/837fb2635548cf9c8f668f33f40006c6.poster.avif?t=1744958119\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348930/extras/837fb2635548cf9c8f668f33f40006c6.webm?t=1744958119\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348930/extras/837fb2635548cf9c8f668f33f40006c6.mp4?t=1744958119\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
